creator: SocialGest LLC
descriptionHtml:
With SocialGest you can schedule your social networks content, optimizing your time and helping you to achieve your goals, to do you social media with greater productivity and efficiency.

Our mobile app will allow you to schedule content on Instagram, Twitter, Facebook and LinkedIn automatically and without notifications that will remind you post manually. You can select a photo from your mobile gallery or use the camera on your device. You can schedule content "once" for an specific date and hour, "several times" between a range of dates with multiple hours, or add it to a cyclic list of posts that you'll need have previously configured in our web app.

In addition you will be able to see your posts that are about to be posted and delete the ones that you don't want to be posted. You will also be able to see the posts that were actually posted.

To learn more about SocialGest and our tools for managing strategies in social networks visit our website www.socialgest.net
